name: Experiment Or Die #71
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. Ever since I was a kid and I saw this movie called "Killer Klowns From Outer Space" I have been deathly afraid of clowns. And fun houses are really not that fun! In the end, you have to face your fears and walk head first into the teeth of the beast. Twitter and IG: Nikejerk.
